  "original_title": "\u0b93\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "President meeting with Ambassador of Oman",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ambassador of Oman to Sri Lanka Ahmed Ali Saeed Al Rasheed has assured President Gotabaya Rajapaksa of support to strengthen bilateral relations between Sri Lanka and Oman in the areas of fuel, gas, energy, employment and investment promotion.",
        "He said this yesterday (01) when he met the President at the Presidential Palace in Fort Colombo before leaving the country after finishing his service as Ambassador to Sri Lanka.",
        "Meanwhile, President Gotabaya Rajapaksa requested the Omani Ambassador to cooperate in increasing job opportunities for Sri Lankan students in Oman.",
        "The President's Media Unit has mentioned that the focus has also been on expanding trade and investment opportunities in the country. (a)"
      ],
